column3: “Fantastic strain for lack of appetite, stress, pain and insomnia. Very uplifting and numbing. Beautiful frosty bud with a cool scent.”
“Amazingly uplifting. This is a 10/10 giggles and munchies strain. Tastes great, looks great. Probably my new favorite strain. If you can get your hands on this you should definitely try it.”
“Definitely a minty smell and flavor. Going to have to try to press some sticky gold out and see how that flavor    really is”
